# Manual Checks Workflow

After every story's verify script passes, append its manual checks to `docs/manual-checks.md`.

## Format

```markdown
## [STORY-ID] — [Story Title]

- [ ] manual check 1
- [ ] manual check 2
- [ ] manual check 3
```

## Rules

- Always append — never overwrite existing entries
- Use the exact story ID from the PRD (e.g. `SETTINGS.1`, `USER.3`, `S0.7`)
- Only include checks that require a live browser, real email, Inngest UI, or production environment — not things the verify script already covers
- Separate sections with `---`
- Create `docs/manual-checks.md` if it does not exist
